/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a car on the road, looking towards the horizon. The sky above is a clear blue, with the sun shining brightly in the top right corner. The street itself is lined with lush green trees and bushes, adding a touch of nature to the urban landscape. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the road, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. Power lines crisscross above, a common sight in many urban areas. The image is taken from a low angle, which gives a sense of depth and scale, drawing the viewer's eye towards the horizon. The colors in the image are vibrant, with the green of the trees and bushes contrasting beautifully with the blue of the sky.
